  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb2\u0bb5\u0b9a\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bc8: \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0b9f\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Not Free: Presidential Action",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Nobody can be given food for free. President Ranil Wickremesinghe also said that if there are government employees who cannot work, such people should be removed immediately.",
        "President Ranil Wickremesinghe said that he is not ready to pay salaries to government employees free of cost.",
        "\u201cNobody can be given free food, something has to be done. I can't eat for free either. If I don't develop this country, I have to go home. Therefore, he said, we ourselves should start the journey first.",
        "I am not calling anyone to rejoin the United National Party. However, President Ranil Wickremesinghe also said that I call on everyone to unite to build the country."
      ],
